response.overview: Well shot film by Chen Yang with a wonderful soundtrack that pulls us in to watch an inviting piece of filmmaking. The sound quality is great and so are the sound effects. The filmmaker is a craftsman and does a great job. In the internal conflict we understand the fragile world she lives in.  Watch it on streamer Montageplay.com
